<plot>Arthur and Cuthbert are rival for fickle Thelma, who fills her cheeks with candy when Cuthbert calls and tells him, from her balcony, that sh has the mumps. Cuthbert tells Arthur, who bandages his face and calls on Thelma, pretending to have the mumps, also. Cuthbert, anxious to call on Thelma, goes to the country hospital and asks the head doctor to give him the mumps germ. The doctor kicks him out but obtains Thelma's address so he can have the house put under quarantine. Many complications follow.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016783</url></doc>
